trans-unit.source: Occurs when the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser"></xref> control has navigated to a new document and has begun loading it.
trans-unit.target: 발생 경우는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser"> </xref> 컨트롤에서 새 문서를 탐색 하 고 로드를 시작한 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control navigates to a new document whenever one of the following properties is set or methods is called: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> Handle the `Navigated` event to receive notification when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control has navigated to a new document.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>컨트롤 속성 중 하나를 설정 또는 메서드가 호출 될 때마다 새 문서를 탐색:- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A>처리는 `Navigated` 이벤트 알림을 받을 때는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>컨트롤이 새 문서를 탐색 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>

trans-unit.source: When the `Navigated` event occurs, the new document has begun loading, which means you can access the loaded content through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 `Navigated` 이벤트가 발생 하면 새 문서를 통해 로드 된 콘텐츠를 액세스할 수 로드가 시작는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>

trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebBrowserArray.DocumentCompleted> event to receive notification when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control finishes loading the new document.

trans-unit.source: You can also receive notification before navigation starts by handling the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebBrowserArray.Navigating> event.

trans-unit.source: Handling this event lets you cancel navigation if certain conditions have not been met, for example, the user has not filled out a form.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 함수 및 개체는 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>네임 스페이스를 Visual Basic 6.0에서의 업그레이드 도구에서 사용 하기 위해 제공 [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 대부분의 경우에서 이러한 함수 및 개체에 다른 네임 스페이스에서 찾을 수 있는 기능이 중복 됩니다.는 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: 필요한 지만 때 Visual Basic 6.0 코드 모델이 크게 다릅니다에서 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] 구현 합니다.
